  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment (W-EP-03 stale input data)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions. COU2 evaluates whether the computational model can predict absolute hemolysis levels for a Class III VAD device at Model Risk Level 5. Monte Carlo uncertainty quantification is performed. All 13 credibility factors are assessed. Decision: Accepted. NOTE: the rheological dataset bound to this assessment carries a dataVintage of 2018-03-15, predating the model revision of 2026-01-10; the narrative does not address whether re-validation against the updated model build was performed.",
